<span id="freeTextContainer11002685520231079122">Chris Wraight is a British author of fantasy and science fiction.<br/><br/>His first novel was published in 2008; since then, he has published books set in the <i>Warhammer Fantasy</i> and <i>Stargate:Atlantis</i> universes, and has upcoming titles in the <i>Warhammer 40K</i> setting.<br/><br/>He is based in the south-west of England.</span>

